    <descript>
      <abstract>This data layer contains points representing culverts located in water networks and marsh areas in Prince William County,VA. Culverts are structures built under travel ways or portions of land allowing water to flow from one side to the other</abstract>
      <purpose>The purpose of this layer is to place a point that graphically represents the location of a culvert in the real world.</purpose>
    </descript>
